in...Jeff Foxworthy. Yes, for the last two years, the world's most
famous redneck _ and I say that with nothing but affection _ has
hosted the TNN Music Awards. Foxworthy will be back for a third
year when the TNN Music Awards, presented for the first time by
Country Weekly magazine, airs live from the 12,000-seat Gaylord
Entertainment Center in Nashville. (Thompson, Palm Beach Post). 25.
