u a BC-OBIT-ASSAD-ABRIDGED-2     06-10 0607
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-OBIT-ASSAD-ABRIDGED-2TAKES-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
HAFEZ ASSAD, WHO TURNED SYRIA INTO A MIDDLE EAST POWER, DIES 
</HEADLINE>
   (DUPLICATION WARNING: Also filed in category ``i'')  
 (EDS: A full-length version, OBIT-ASSAD-ABRIDGED, is also being
filed. See also: ASSAD-DEATH)  
