<HEADER>
A0418 &Cx1f; tab-z
u k BC-ASSAD-BUDGET-(JUNE10)     06-10 0490
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ASSAD-BUDGET-(JUNE10)-NYTSF </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   &UR; (EDITORS: IN THE WAKE OF SYRIAN PRESIDENT HAFEZ AL-ASSAD'S SUDDEN
