   MLK-CONSPIRACY _ ATLANTA _ A 22-month investigation by the
Department of Justice concluded Friday that there is no evidence of
a conspiracy in the April 1968 assassination of the Rev. Martin
Luther King Jr. (Bryce, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). MOVED
Friday.
</P>
