province and ended a campaign by Serb and Yugoslav authorities to
wipe out its Albanian majority and ethnically cleanse a whole
people. Twelve months into the peacekeeping mission, the basic
rhythms of surging U.S. economy is translating into some extra
dollars for overseas tourists. Americans in Paris, London Berlin
and other European locations are finding these days that their
purchasing power has increased here along with the value of the
greenback. Developing. (Roughton, Cox News Service). WITH PHOTOS.
