 &UR; (mexican presidential election preview) &QL; 
TRADE _ Arizona businesses, investors and trade experts are
wondering what a victory by the National Action Party (PAN) on July
2 could mean for their fragile cross-border partnership with
Mexico. Story will move in the ``A'' category.
</P>
